Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}True Calendar Year 70\NSakimori Academy Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To all of our new students,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,congratulations on being \Nadmitted to Sakimori Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On this beautiful Spring day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you have embarked on a new chapter in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your lives as Sakimori Academy students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as your senpai in school, as \Nwell as in life to some degree,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and am sincerely happy to be \Nable to learn alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might sometimes have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,misgivings about this new, strict \Nlife away from your families,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it might seem stiff \Nand formal sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no memories of anything up \Nuntil middle school. That's why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the next town over from mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I couldn't make small \Ntalk like everybody else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know anything about myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I a kindhearted \Nperson? Am I cheerful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's my family like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do I have friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are my favorite things?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before I talked to anyone else, I \Nhad my hands full talking to myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"What kind of person is Marie Nobi?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that was always a \Nquestion without an answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Why don't we go today, then? \N- Can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I wanted to check out \Nsome accessories, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, that store has all kinds of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, their stuff is super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie... I don't believe it, you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie Nobi. Did you pilot a Valvrave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This much power, just from \Nadapting the Valvrave tech...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Cain... The Valvraves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both go way beyond human understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X! Fall back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used up this much energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yamada! Get up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're Kamitsuki remember? \NYou aren't dead, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But my temperature's \Nmaxed out. I can't move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Löwenglitzen emission test complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deviation from theoretical \Nvalues, 0.007%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant X-eins, proceed to Phase \N8 after replacing energy pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blitzendegen. Will replace energy pack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call dibs on a Kirschbaum \Nnext time, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All forces, we're pulling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir? The place I saw the \NJIORans is farther up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of L-elf's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Valvraves are probably \Nlying in ambush up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go around issuing orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I have command authority here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-elf's plan was to lure the \Nenemy out onto this plateau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- It's too great a risk.\N - What is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then use bombs to collapse \Nthe ground out from under them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He not only knows this terrain \Nlike the back of his hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's also trying to exploit \None of its features.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to risk it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its features?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}There should be five Valvraves, \Nbut there are only two here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He has a reason for committing \Nonly a small force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-drei? You're Lunar Orbital \NNavy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must be trying to bait us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-neun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-elf is hiding in that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bomb it from the air and \Ncollapse the bedrock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Settling things once and for all \Nwhere we all shared in that sin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you feel the hand of fate at work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something happening up top?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is there who knows \Nboth me and this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only catch half of \Nthem, but we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Podded missile volley, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf... Don't tell me \Nyou had the same idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvraves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard that they \Nhave come down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And where did you hear this \Nbit of information from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do have one or two friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you have dreams of \Nthis country of students?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-drei, where are you?! A-drei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie? L-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvrave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry. I no longer have \Nany intention of shooting you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've been completely \Ntrapped by the cave-in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our only way out is to use Unit 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear you. I'm just a \Nlittle overwhelmed right now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wound, it's healed... Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about your own body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know. I'm like Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. What kind of human am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I missing memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Memories?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I only have two \Nyears' worth of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're that... from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It melted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't we heard from L-elf yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't checked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Units 3 and 5 that \Nare the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Haruto's Unit 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous! We're \Nwaiting here for L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still no signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm ready and \Nwaiting to hack the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't handle all these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The army's trying to save face, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, we seem to be doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-eins! H-neun! We're falling back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective is simply the operational \Ntesting of the Kirschbaums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, as much as I hate to say \Nit, we don't have jurisdiction here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, K-zwölf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, K-zwölf!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-zwölf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-zwölf...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent out a rescue signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't mastered mental \Ncontrol yet, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry, I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I gonna do? The plan is a bust!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't even try to contact the \Nothers, not with this guy here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you step to your right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've stumbled across something \Nthat really takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you are doing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underwent Karlstein \Ntraining in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then certain facts came to light \Nand I was forced to kill a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right here on this shoreline.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My friend was a Royalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, he had ties \Nto the old government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the military found \Nout that a traitor to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the current regime was \Na member of our team,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the team would be put \Non trial for his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-neun. X-eins. Q-vier. Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A capital offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we killed \Nour friend in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"If you are going to be killed, kill."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that my friend carved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pino is Marie's friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friend? My friend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1796 days ago, you and I first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Valvraves were completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and I were in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were a test pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what they called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My vessel was still very \Nsmall back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You climbed into me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lonely, too! So let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? I don't know \Nabout any experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I ate them. The information \Nyou call memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Consumed? Used?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Information? You mean Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The elementary particles of information.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. The information that \Nhumans possess is memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the reason I have no memories is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! We're falling back to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Runes. My food. I use \Nthem whenever I move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Formless. Invisible. Energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe it, you ate my memories?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school entrance ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakimori Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did I get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry trees were blooming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! I can't \Nremember anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do at the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... used Runes just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Valvraves and my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now my oldest memory just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Units 3 and 5 are taking a pounding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unit 3 cooled down but still can't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unit 5 is almost out of spare \NImpact Booster coolers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My brother and the others \Nhave been found, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Units 4 and 6 are out of action! \NThat just leaves Unit 1!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I use this... I'll forget even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you to run, Senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't leave you here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Operate Unit 1, Marie Nobi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't, your classmates \Nwill be wiped out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only have two years of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The heat buildup isn't stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't Unit 3 cool down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't hurt him any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children have nothing \Nto do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I talked them into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry out there! Save them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's Unit 1?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-elf!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I pilot it... I'll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make new ones, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't create a past, but you \Ncan make all kinds of futures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futures?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make some future \Nmemories together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, together! Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 1! Who's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Committing one more \Nwon't save them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush them, Blume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! It can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima. Let's \Nget to the transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made Marie pilot it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was Unit 1's original pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! He can bring \Nup that kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can make new memories \Nand friendships,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to go on fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, you are broken! \NYour limiter is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are losing lots of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were \Nfired! As test pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gap! Loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Resume operation. We're \Nstealing this transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they shatter, \NI can make new ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's the signal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go 15 meters clockwise down \Ncorridor 18, then go right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you're through the authentication \Ngate and security door,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}go straight 30 meters, then left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're five blocks from the bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay! I'm okay! I'm still okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Control established over transport. \NRemaining enemy blocks, 12%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm being hacked?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ladies and gentlemen of \NNew JIOR, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are the Dorssian Royalists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are prepared to offer you assistance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Royalists?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Set your course to magnetic \Nbearing 37 and—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're lifting off. We'll \Nretrieve Unit 1 in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep an eye outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Units 3 and 5 have landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thermal runaway phenomenon \Nthat the Lunar Orbital Navy reported!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marie! Marie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you okay? You aren't hurt, are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course I'm your friend!\N What are you talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are there more here? More friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your best friends are here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"They're idiots, but some might \Nturn out to be geniuses."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who said that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... They must \Nreally have liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I had friends like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marie, what happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had friends who meant that much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's even bigger than it was in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marie! Marie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you okay? Marie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong? Come on, answer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie... Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 17, "The Rune Abyss."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system that will expose \Nthe truth of the world.